original_title: T.K. Kirkland: Who Raised You? Comedy Special
overview: T.K. Kirkland is an underground comedic legend bringing you the laughs with his one-night-only stand-up comedy special, "Who Raised You?" Kirkland uses real-life situations as his canvas and paints vivid pictures with his storytelling and jokes.
title: T.K. Kirkland: Who Raised You? Comedy Special
